thread.title: LaVern in West Laurel
thread.title_full: Any Assembly reviewed by LaVern in West Laurel

author: LaVern in West Laurel
title: LaVern in West Laurel
text: Any Assembly was wonderful. They recently put together a 3-drawer credenza in the time estimated and did not scoff at my "smaller" handyman needs. Some handyman companies avoid you when you have needs that are not big money makers. Any Assembly does not do this. Because of this my husband paid them a bit more. We are always very pleased with their work.
